<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">صـ ٣٦ / س ٨:</span> <span class="c1">"الجيلي"</span> تعدل: <span class="c1">"الجبلي"</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">صـ ١٨٨ / س ٦:</span> <span class="c1">"الفضل"</span> تعدل: <span class="c1">"حفص"</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">صـ ٢٣٥:</span> هامش <span class="c2">(٣)</span>: <span class="c1">"التركذي"</span> تعدل: <span class="c1">"الترمذي"</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">صـ ٣٩٧ / س الأخير:</span> <span class="c1">"الفضل"</span> تعدل: <span class="c1">"حفص"</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
